## BP-004-A01: Assemble component context

test TC-A01-01 "Context includes the component definition"
  verifies: BP-004-A01
  given: a SystemModel with component COMP-001
  when: Assemble is called
  expect: the AgentContext for COMP-001 has a component field
          whose id is "COMP-001"

test TC-A01-02 "Context includes allocated derived requirements"
  verifies: BP-004-A01
  given: REQ-A-01 has allocated_to COMP-001 and REQ-B-01 has
         allocated_to COMP-002
  when: Assemble is called
  expect: AgentContext for COMP-001 contains REQ-A-01 but not
          REQ-B-01 in its requirements list

test TC-A01-03 "Context includes verifying test specs"
  verifies: BP-004-A01
  given: TC-001 verifies REQ-A-01 which is allocated_to COMP-001,
         and TC-002 verifies REQ-B-01 which is allocated_to COMP-002
  when: Assemble is called
  expect: AgentContext for COMP-001 contains TC-001 but not TC-002

test TC-A01-04 "One context per component"
  verifies: BP-004-A01
  given: a SystemModel with three components
  when: Assemble is called
  expect: the returned list has three AgentContexts, one per
          component, indexed by component id

## BP-004-A02: Resolve interface references

test TC-A02-01 "Interfaces list is populated"
  verifies: BP-004-A02
  given: a SystemModel with two interface definitions
  when: Assemble is called
  expect: each AgentContext's interfaces list contains both
          definitions

test TC-A02-02 "Every referenced interface type is present"
  verifies: BP-004-A02
  given: a component whose requirements reference interface
         names that exist in the model
  when: Assemble is called
  expect: every referenced interface name in the context's
          requirements resolves to a full InterfaceDefinition
          in the same context

## BP-004-A03: Include system requirement intent

test TC-A03-01 "Parent system requirements accompany derived requirements"
  verifies: BP-004-A03
  given: REQ-001 is a system-level requirement and REQ-001-A
         derives from it with allocated_to COMP-001
  when: Assemble is called
  expect: AgentContext for COMP-001 contains both REQ-001-A
          and REQ-001

test TC-A03-02 "System requirements listed in satisfies are included"
  verifies: BP-004-A03
  given: COMP-001 has satisfies: REQ-001 and REQ-001 has no
         derived requirements yet
  when: Assemble is called
  expect: AgentContext for COMP-001 contains REQ-001

test TC-A03-03 "Parent requirement included only once when multiple derived reqs share it"
  verifies: BP-004-A03
  given: REQ-001 has two derived requirements both allocated to
         COMP-001
  when: Assemble is called
  expect: AgentContext for COMP-001 contains REQ-001 exactly
          once in its requirements list

## BP-008-A01: Assemble only affected components

test TC-A08-01 "AssembleOnly returns only the listed components"
  verifies: BP-008-A01
  given: a SystemModel with three components A, B, C and the
         affected list is ["A", "C"]
  when: AssembleOnly is called
  expect: the returned list contains AgentContexts for A and C
          only, with B omitted

test TC-A08-02 "AssembleOnly with empty list returns empty"
  verifies: BP-008-A01
  given: a SystemModel with three components and an empty
         affected list
  when: AssembleOnly is called
  expect: the returned list is empty

test TC-A08-03 "AssembleOnly ignores unknown component ids"
  verifies: BP-008-A01
  given: a SystemModel with components A and B, and the
         affected list is ["A", "UNKNOWN"]
  when: AssembleOnly is called
  expect: the returned list contains only the AgentContext
          for A, and no error occurs
